    "## 7. Summary\n\n| Model | Dice | IoU | Notes |\n|-------|:----:|:---:|-------|\n| U-Net (original, from scratch) | ~0.48 | ~0.31 | Dice loss only |\n| U-Net (improved, EfficientNetB0) | >0.75 | >0.60 | Combined loss + attention |\n| Mask R-CNN | 0.22 | 0.14 | Pre-trained, not fine-tuned |\n| Random Forest | ~0.47 | ~0.32 | RGB+LBP features |\n\n**Key bug fixed**: Comparison loop showed U-Net Dice=0.03 due to filename mismatch (`unet_mask_1.png` ≠ `mask_ar037_...png`). Real Dice was 0.48.\n\n**Next steps**: Run `python src/train.py --config config.yaml` to train the improved model and target Dice > 0.75."
